headline: Up Over 60% in the Past Year, Is It Too Late to Buy AT&T Stock?
summary: The giant telecom has been succeeding even as rival Verizon has been struggling.  The stock trades at elevated levels, but may not be all that expensive relative to earnings.  AT&T (NYSE: T) is a leading telecom company in the country -- and as it has exited the streaming and media businesses and refocused on its core operations, it has been proving to be a solid investment again.
